既定参数url：the full URL being accessed.host：the hostname extracted from the URL.  it is the exact same string as between :&#x2F;&#x2F; and the first : or &#x2F; after that. The port number is not included in this parameter. It can be extracted from the URL when necessary.ret：(the return value) a string describing the configuration. The format of this string is defined below. 
